data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, space, and seclusion in this charming double-wide trailer situated on over 1 acre. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with a unique feature - two of the bathrooms are conveniently located in the master bedroom, offering lots of space and privacy. Escape the urban hustle and experience the peacefulness of this property,  positioned outside city limits. Revel in the freedom of country living while maintaining accessibility to nearby amenities. Schedule your showing today.
